WEBVTT

00:06.000 --> 00:12.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

00:25.830 --> 00:27.150
Mr Leonard, sir!

00:28.950 --> 00:30.829
Sahib?

00:30.830 --> 00:31.990
Sahib?

00:33.230 --> 00:34.270
Sahib!

00:38.790 --> 00:39.950
What is it?

00:41.790 --> 00:43.429
What do you want?

00:43.430 --> 00:46.589
I was pruning the hedges
in the garden,

00:46.590 --> 00:48.310
and I saw something terrible.

00:51.670 --> 00:54.470
Mr Leonard, I'm afraid you
are going to die today.

00:57.428 --> 01:18.166
